snippet.title: PhoboPhobia Game Announcement Teaser | Oxtail Games
snippet.description:
Welcome to PhoboPhobia! A game by Oxtail Games.

The game is currently under development. You can try it at itch.io: https://oxtail-games.itch.io/phobo-phobia
Visit the official web and discover more! https://oxtailgames.com/

Share this video and help me reach more people!

Follow all social networks for updates on the development:
https://x.com/OxtailGames
https://www.instagram.com/oxtailgames/
https://www.tiktok.com/@oxtailgames
https://www.reddit.com/r/OxtailGames/
https://www.youtube.com/@OxtailGames 

Join the community: https://discord.gg/aYyZK5asFq
Support the development!: patreon.com/OxtailGames

Thanks for your support!!
